Author: HappierHungry
Text: lol my mum was recently like "yes, I did suspect you may have had some issues so I just tried to keep an eye on you"  ???  as if I hadn't been obviously unwell/miserable for most of my life??? and would have appreciated some support???  and how she's phrasing it like she *thought* I had issues but she was *wrong*, because I'm clearly *fine*???   thanks, mum.
